## ðŸ§ª Empirical Backing

> Based on Thesis C (Krecklenberg, 2023)

- ðŸ“Š 41% of enterprise use-case prompts triggered hallucinations
- ðŸ§  70% corrected with **human intervention**
- ðŸŽ¯ 94% relevance success rate after skew removal

**Conclusion**: Human-led relevance correction outperforms static RLHF or fine-tuning for context-variant tasks.

